Enum Class Characters

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Characters>
Characters
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Characters>, Constable
public enum Characters extends Enum<Characters>
Enum for the characters in the game. The characters are: Pico - a bird Milo - a cat Bailey - a dog Luna - a dog Finn - a fish Bubbles - a fish Sparx - a robot Byte - a robot Gizmo - a robot
